IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_STParcel') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STParcel
GO

    [lms_parcel_barcode] nvarchar(4000),
    [lms_parcel_volweight] float,

	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],

	)
GO
